{"tid":210782,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"多蒙特受襲原因水落石出","createTime":"2017-04-21T07:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T11:50:44.000Z","uid":2538,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10f65d69d2ba137496bdcc7abe28c4ba7a63787d","tid":210782,"uid":2538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T07:53:04.000Z","msg":"水落石出！德國檢察官發表官方聲明，已經逮捕多蒙特炸彈客，疑犯係擁有德俄雙重國籍嘅28歲男子，因為買左15000多蒙特股票嘅Put輪(股票愈跌愈賺錢)，而有預謀地策劃襲擊，事前已預訂該星期及下星期多蒙特會入住嘅酒店(因預訂當時未知幾時踢主場)。<br />\n<br />\n事發時疑犯相信喺酒店「欣賞」爆炸，並留低同寄出多封模仿中東恐怖組織或德國極右份子嘅信件，以圖迷惑警方調查，相信係單獨行事。查看紀錄，多蒙特股價由4月11日收市5.61，跌至最新5.36，跌幅達4.4%。<br />\n<br />\n炒股票炒到襲擊足球運動員，實在可恥！"},{"pid":"1d1e1086f52b2bcd2796f5eba1c34ddde6a8826e","tid":210782,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:09:47.000Z","msg":"好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de19cabc2909303b29caa392b28be0ddeac91ba","tid":210782,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:10:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29d4a3b1e7022dc868021510c7fb9e66cd76d52e","tid":210782,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:11:40.000Z","msg":"好撚仆街"},{"pid":"845e89d174f5ca41cabdb4f2cf6417e3defd66fd","tid":210782,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:11:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚仆街</blockquote><br />\n唔及你"},{"pid":"4992552fcd823fcff22033b4d690ef0b82f80888","tid":210782,"uid":52675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:13:19.000Z","msg":"背後肯定有金主啦"},{"pid":"0f81e8ae81ae73c8d212bb6f89b8ad0dd6f14978","tid":210782,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:13:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好撚仆街</blockquote><br />\n唔及你</blockquote><br />\n你收聲啦"},{"pid":"5b578eae6c2c4ba0981722e6e98208db3f9002da","tid":210782,"uid":107417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:15:03.000Z","msg":"